description:
All 24 apartments in the building are full-time Airbnb's and hosted by me!

*Surgery friendly 

This property is right next to the airport! If you’re in Miami and looking for convenience, location and want to enjoy the city with all it’s possibilities but have to stick to a tight budget look no further! Minutes away from the beach, sports venues, world renowned medical facilities, port of Miami, downtown and more! It is my goal provide a home for you during your stay!


I’m available to my guests at any time before and during their stay! This starts with the inquiry and ends at checkout, I’m committed to providing the best possible service at all times!
